- Antecedent, behavior, consequence
- Positive reinforcement
- Competing behavior pathway
</Markdown>

<Markdown id="fba2_email_rubric">
### Email Rubric

Your email will be evaluated on:
1. Does it specify changes to **antecedent conditions** that will make it easier to get the child to bed on time?
2. Does it specify changes to **consequence conditions** that will make it easier to get the child to bed on time?
3. Are the interventions proposed ones that the psychological literature recommends as effective in addressing sleep refusal?
4. Does the email provide enough **detail** about the interventions that the babysitter will be able to implement the plan effectively?
</Markdown>

<TextArea id="fba2_email_to_roommate" rows="10" placeholder="Write your email to Annie's roommate describing the new intervention plan..." />

